com.horse.pokemon.GraphicsEngine.ScreenEngine

Class MainGameScreen

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.horse.pokemon.GraphicsEngine.ScreenEngine.MainGameScreen
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.badlogic.gdx.Screen

    public class MainGameScreen
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.badlogic.gdx.Screen
    Class containing all the graphical pieces for when the User is on the screen state. This is the Screen that is used the most as the major actions happen on this screen.
    See Also:
